{
  "stem": "7094.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She would say  that, look, if we are in a cage-- we're going into a ghetto-- we'll be closed in-- I can't help you, and you can't help me.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But if you are outside, you've always managed to help.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You've always showed resourcefulness.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You will be able to help me more outside than inside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There, again, I don't know how much of this was her persuasion and how much was this instinct for life.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I'm still not sure which of the two was the prevalent.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I remember we walked back and forwards, between the house of this woman, and I didn't want to say goodbye.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "On the last day, she didn't even answer my door.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She didn't want to see me-- [DRINKS] my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I went with this woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was beginning of November, already frosty cold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We walked, because we didn't have-- we didn't have any facilities to travel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we walked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This was about-- quite a long walk, 60 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[SNIFFS] And I arrived to this village where her daughter lived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And she introduced me there as Olga Demczyzszak.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "This-- I was her neighbor's daughter who came here to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And Zosia was going to come.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Now Zosia, when she met this situation, realized the danger.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "This woman didn't realize the danger she was in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "She was naive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "She didn't realize.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Nobody did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But this was about-- not far from Belzec.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she knew what was going-- not exactly, but in this village somebody was shot with full documents.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so she said, mother, what have you done?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I-- and she didn't want to go back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was resigned to go back to Jaworow, to join my mother in ghetto, because I wasn't very-- and we were going to get ready to go back.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
